        <div n="M023090A" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-1">While maudlin Whigs deplord th<hi rend="sup">ṛ</hi> Cato's fate</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-2"> Still with dry Eyes the Tory Celia sate,</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-3"> But while her pride forbids her Tears <add>to</add> flow,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-4"> The gushing Waters find a Vent below;</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-5"> Tho' secret yet with copious Grief She mourns</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-6"> Like Twenty river Gods with all their Urns,</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-7"> Let others screw their Hypocritick face</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-8"> She shews her Grief in a sincerer place</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-9"> There Nature reigns and Passion void of Art,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-M023090A-line-10"> For that road leads directly to the HeartM023090A   </l></lg></div>
      </div>
